"Q3". "Difference between Regression and Retesting?"
Answer:
Retesting → Verify fixed defect
Regression → Ensure existing functionality is unaffected
  
"Q4. What are Smoke and Sanity Testing?"
Answer:
Smoke → Broad level testing of critical functionalities
Sanity → Narrow level testing after small changes

