"Q6. What is Hoisting?"

Answer:

JavaScript moves declarations to the top during compilation.

console.log(a);
var a = 10;

Equivalent
var a;
console.log(a);
a = 10;

"Q7. Difference between == and ===?"
Answer:
== → compares values only
=== → compares value + datatype

Example:
5 == "5"   // true
5 === "5"  // false


